---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Launch Storyboard | ForgeLens"
  description="A ready storyboard for shipping a clear ForgeLens launch demo."
>
  <section class="shell section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <h2>Launch storyboard for a sharp product demo.</h2>
      <p>
        Show the pain, run ForgeLens, then show the AI reading risky files first. Keep it short, clear,
        and evidence-based.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="demo-panel">
      <div class="terminal" aria-label="Demo script command block">
        <span class="muted">$</span> forgelens scan --format all --out .forgelens<br />
        <span class="muted">$</span> forgelens baseline save --name main<br />
        <span class="muted">$</span> forgelens drift --git main..HEAD<br />
        <span class="muted">$</span> cat .forgelens/DRIFT_REPORT.md<br /><br />
        <span class="muted">Talk track:</span><br />
        1) Show risky files before edit<br />
        2) Explain why auth and data paths are first<br />
        3) Start AI work from ranked list
      </div>
      <div class="video-placeholder" aria-label="Launch narrative card">
        <div>
          <span class="label">45-second launch cut</span>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 12px;">From repo noise to risk-first AI guidance.</h3>
          <p class="small" style="margin-top: 12px;">
            Sequence: problem, scan, drift, compact context, agent result. End with reliability and speed.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="play" aria-hidden="true">GO</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
